<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ lʿmq ḥb rby .. dẖạq ʿny mwt ạlṣlb
 fkẖlṣny .. mṭhraⁿạ qlby
 wmn frṭ ḥb .. rby str ạ̹tẖmy wʿyby
 hllwyạ .. qd mḥạ dẖnby
 ạlqrạr- hllwyạ qd fdạny .. wbdmh ạ̹sẖtrạny
 wmn kl ạ̹tẖmiⁿ .. qd ḥrrny
 sykwn lḥn qlby .. ạlmjd dwmaⁿạ lrby
 hllwyạ .. qd mḥạ dẖnby
 2- mn ʿmq jb ạlkẖṭyẗ .. ạ̹ly̱ ạlrạḥẗ ạlbhyẗ
 qd rfʿny .. mkẖlṣaⁿạ nfsy
 mn kẖṭạyạyạ ạlʿdydẗ .. ạ̹ly̱ ạlḥyạẗ ạljdydẗ
 hllwyạ .. qd mḥạ dẖnby</lyrics>
